    <fr:addr type="user">plt-semantics-0003</fr:addr>
    <fr:route>plt-semantics-0003.xml</fr:route>
    <fr:title text="Operational semantics">Operational semantics</fr:title>
    <fr:authors />
  </fr:frontmatter>
  <fr:mainmatter>
    <fr:p>The <fr:em>operational semantics</fr:em> defines the meaning of terms in a langauge <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[T]]></fr:tex> using an
<fr:em>execution relation</fr:em> that specifies how terms can be executed in an appropriate machine
model.</fr:p>
    <fr:p>There are two forms of operations semantics:

<fr:ul><fr:li><fr:strong>small-step operational semantics</fr:strong> which describes the individual execution steps</fr:li>
<fr:li><fr:strong>big-step operational semantics</fr:strong> which describes the overall results of execution</fr:li></fr:ul></fr:p>
    <fr:tree toc="true" numbered="true" show-heading="true" show-metadata="false" expanded="true" root="false" xmlns:fr="http://www.jonmsterling.com/jms-005P.xml">
      <fr:frontmatter>
        <fr:anchor>438</fr:anchor>
        <fr:addr type="user">plt-semantics-0005</fr:addr>
        <fr:route>plt-semantics-0005.xml</fr:route>
        <fr:title text="Small-step operation semantics">Small-step operation semantics</fr:title>
        <fr:authors />
      </fr:frontmatter>
      <fr:mainmatter>
        <fr:p>A small-step semantics for a language ${T} of syntactic terms comprises two components:

<fr:ul><fr:li>a set of <fr:em>execution states</fr:em> <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[S]]></fr:tex></fr:li>
<fr:li>a <fr:em>transition relation</fr:em> <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[s \rightarrow  s']]></fr:tex> on <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[S]]></fr:tex> that relates each state
<fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[s]]></fr:tex> to each state <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[s']]></fr:tex> that may be reached by performaing a single execution step</fr:li></fr:ul></fr:p>
      </fr:mainmatter>
      <fr:backmatter />
    </fr:tree>
  </fr:mainmatter>
  <fr:backmatter>
    <fr:tree toc="false" numbered="false" show-heading="true" show-metadata="false" expanded="true" root="false" xmlns:fr="http://www.jonmsterling.com/jms-005P.xml">
      <fr:frontmatter>
        <fr:title text="Backlinks">Backlinks</fr:title>
